NAME
    Music::Tag::LyricsFetcher - Plugin module for Music::Tag to fetch lyrics
    use Lyrics::Fetcher

INSTALLATION
    To install this module type the following:

       perl Makefile.PL
       make
       make test
       make install

DEPENDENCIES
    This module requires these other modules and libraries:

       Music::Tag
       Lyrics::Fetcher
       Lyrics::Fetcher::LeosLyrics

    You can also install these other plugins

        Lyrics::Fetcher::LyricWiki
        Lyrics::Fetcher::AZLyrics
        Lyrics::Fetcher::AstraWeb

SOURCE
    Source is available at github:
    http://github.com/riemann42/Music-Tag-LyricsFetcher.

BUGTRACKING
    Please use github for bug tracking:
    http://github.com/riemann42/Music-Tag-LyricsFetcher/issues.

